            <h2 class="heading">Problem Statement</h2>
            <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--neutral-700);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;">Space Force software factories face systemic challenges that impede mission delivery:</p>
            <div class="grid-2">
              <div style="padding:14px;background:#fef2f2;border:1px solid #fecaca;border-radius:6px;">
